        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "=<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#f6f7f9;padding:24px 0;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><tr><td align=\"center\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #eceef2;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\"><tr><td style=\"background:#047857;padding:20px 28px;\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;\">Gepromed</span><span style=\"color:#bbf7d0;font-size:12px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Place confirmée</span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:28px;color:#1f2430;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;\">Félicitations {{ $('Supabase · lead updated').item.json.body.record.first_name }},</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;\">Votre inscription à <b>{{ $('Supabase · lead updated').item.json.body.record.training_title_snapshot }}</b> est confirmée (référence {{ $('Supabase · lead updated').item.json.body.record.ref }}).</p><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#ecfdf5;border:1px solid #a7f3d0;border-radius:10px;margin:8px 0 18px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 18px;\"><div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#047857;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px;\">Vos accès à la plateforme de formation (Gepromed LMS)</div><div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#0f172a;\">Identifiant : <b>{{ $('Supabase · lead updated').item.json.body.record.lms_user_id }}</b></div><div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#0f172a;\">Mot de passe temporaire : <b>gepromed-{{ $('Supabase · lead updated').item.json.body.record.ref }}</b></div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#66728a;margin-top:6px;\">À modifier lors de votre première connexion.</div></td></tr></table><p style=\"margin:0;color:#66728a;font-size:13px;\">Vous recevrez un mot de bienvenue un à deux jours avant le début de la formation.</p><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:1px solid #eceef2;margin:22px 0;\"><p style=\"margin:0;color:#66728a;font-size:13px;\"><b style=\"color:#42495c;\">English:</b> Your seat for {{ $('Supabase · lead updated').item.json.body.record.training_title_snapshot }} is confirmed. Your Gepromed LMS login is above. Please change the temporary password on your first sign-in.</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"background:#f6f7f9;border-top:1px solid #eceef2;padding:18px 28px;color:#66728a;font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;\"><b style=\"color:#42495c;\">Gepromed</b>, Institut de formation chirurgicale<br>2 rue Marie Hamm, 67000 Strasbourg, France<br>Téléphone : +33 3 88 00 00 00 &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Email : formation@gepromed.com</td></tr></table></td></tr></table>",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "b5555555-5555-4555-8555-555555555555",
